					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">All sprites are 8 pixels wide and one of 8 or 16 pixels tall, selectable at any time (but is shared across all sprites).<br />Each sprite has three colors, plus transparent.<br />Each sprite can choose one of four three-color palettes, entirely separate from the background.<br />Multiple sprites can be overlapped.<br />Games almost always combine multiple sprites (even without overlap) in order to make something larger; on this forum we call those things &quot;metasprites&quot;</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

